node.text: From Father’s Day to reconnecting with family and friends, this summer will surely be one to remember….personally, I’ll be crafting memories with one of my family’s favorite recipes, a Mojo Roasted Prime Rib…simple, exquisite ingredients give balance to this delicious dish, and there's no better companion while I'm in the kitchen than a glass of my favorite @DiplomaticoRum Reserva Exclusiva...on the rocks….cheers! #TheHeartOfRum

node.text: EXCITING NEWS‼️...I’m teaming up with my go-to @diplomaticorum to bring you #TheHeartOfRum!...Diplomático’s passion for crafting their family of rums really reflects my lifelong love of cooking (and cocktails!) with simple yet sublime ingredients and attention to detail...and what better way to toast to this partnership than with one of my all-time favorite drinks: a Diplomático Daiquiri...Enjoy!

node.text:
Today the @JacquesPepinFoundation released Cook with Jacques & Friends: Volume 2 and I’m proud to have a recipe featured in the Video Recipe Book. For many chefs, Jacques is a mentor who is generous beyond compare. His foundation supports free culinary and life skills training to individuals in desperate need. Everyone who joins the JPF receives access to Volume 2, as well as Volume 1, featuring 100 recipes from top chefs and bartenders around the country. Membership starts at $40/year. Sign up yourself, or give the gift of membership with this unique virtual platform.

Cook along with us while supporting a great cause. Join here: https://members.jp.foundation. Thank you and #happycooking! 

#jacquespepin #jacquespepinfoundation #JPFmember #videorecipebook #communitykitchen #payitforward #cookingathome

node.text: Very excited to tell you guys that my new book FIX IT WITH FOOD: EVERY MEAL EASY is coming out this December!…I was inspired by how many of you enjoyed the first book…plus the response to my “Symon Dinners” series last year…I became passionate about creating a cookbook of simple weekday breakfasts, lunches, and dinners….just like in the first FIX IT WITH FOOD, these meals address autoimmune triggers with 125 new recipes for everyone who wants to feel better without compromising eating well…including  an all-new 10 day, 30-recipe reset to identify your own triggers!…excited to hear what you guys think….Link in bio to preorder 📚
